BEGIN_DESC
# Mesh Debug

A small utility for developers. Meshdebug can be used to visually identify a mesh group in a vessel mesh. Set the camera
focus on the vessel whose meshes you want to inspect. Then open the mesh debugger dialog from the Custom functions list
(Ctrl-F4). The vessel meshes will become semi-transparent, and the selected mesh group will blink.
END_DESC
